ees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.331948, "shard": "06", "shelf_id": "sn83002748, 1920-09-23, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/wyu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["saratoga", "saratoga (wyo.)", "carbon county (wyo.)", "united states", "carbon", "newspapers", "wyoming"], "subject_headings": ["Saratoga (Wyo.)--Newspapers", "Carbon County (Wyo.)--Newspapers", "United States--Wyoming--Carbon--Saratoga"], "subjects": [{"carbon": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:carbon&fo=json"}, {"carbon county (wyo.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:carbon+county+%28wyo.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"saratoga": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:saratoga&fo=json"}, {"saratoga (wyo.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:saratoga+%28wyo.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"wyoming": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:wyoming&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-06-28T05:57:28.643Z", "title": "The Saratoga sun (Saratoga, Carbon County, Wyo.), September 23, 1920", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83002748/1920-09-23/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://lccn.loc.gov/sn83002748", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83002748/", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/4a126194-059b-549a-8583-d7b45c5f7cc5"], "batch": ["wyu_diamondville_ver05"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1891", "description": ["Weekly Vol. 1, no. 1 (July 14, 1891)- Daily ed.: Saratoga daily sun, <July 4, 1891>."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:02.120Z"